    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>stock<strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>sugar </strong>to the pan&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Drain and rinse the<strong> butter&nbsp;</strong><strong>beans</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>butter</strong>&nbsp;<strong>beans</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>water </strong>to the pan and cook over a medium-low heat for 15-20 min &ndash; this is your <strong>tomato-bean mix</strong></p>",
