    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim and slice the <strong>spring onions&nbsp;</strong>finely</p>\r\n<p>Chop the<strong> parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Crumble the <strong>feta</strong> into a mixing bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>spring onion</strong> and half of the <strong>parsley</strong> (you'll use the rest later) and mix together</p>\r\n<p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>&ndash;&nbsp;this is your <strong>feta</strong>&nbsp;<strong>filling</strong></p>",
